oads/2024/08/stephen-curry-drake@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/stephen-curry-drake@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/stephen-curry-drake@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> NBA 球星斯蒂芬·库里透露，他仍然是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/drake">德雷克</a>的忠实支持者，即使在今年早些时候这位说唱歌手与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">肯德里克·拉马尔</a>发生争执之后也是如此。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/drake-and-kendrick-lamars-feud-the-full-timeline-3754820">德雷克和肯德里克·拉马尔的不和：完整的时间表</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.gq.com/story/stephen-curry-mr-throwback-set-visit" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在接受<em>GQ</em>采访时</a>，这位过去几年与德雷克建立了友谊的金州勇士队控球后卫被问及他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/drake-and-kendrick-lamars-feud-the-full-timeline-3754820">德雷克与拉马尔之间不</a>和的看法。</p><p>在这场争执中，拉马尔在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-responds-to-kendrick-lamar-diss-with-family-matters-lamar-drops-meet-the-grahams-an-hour-later-3753494">《拜见格雷厄姆一家》</a>中点名了这位篮球运动员，并提出了对德雷克恋童癖的指控：“<em>嘿，库里，让家人远离我/对于任何体现对孩子的爱的人，让家人远离我们。”走开/如果你站在他身边，他们也会看着你，让家人远离</em>。”</p><p>库里对<em>《GQ》杂志</em>说：“我是德雷克的大佬。我已经呆了很长时间了。我想显然你知道说唱行业拥有这样的东西意味着什么，但我仍然和德雷克一起摇滚。绝对地。绝对地。” </p><figure id="attachment_3762140" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3762140" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3762140" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/drake@2000x1270.jpg" alt="德雷克现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/drake@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/drake@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/drake@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/drake@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, htt